parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the PODS can cause the airbag system to malfunction, leading to the deactivation of the passenger airbag, which can increase the risk of injury or death in the event of a crash.
symptoms: The passenger airbag off light stays on
even when an adult is seated in the passenger seat; the airbag system fails to detect the presence of a passenger; the airbag system intermittently detects the presence of a passenger.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle hesitates or fails to shift gears
the transmission slips or jerks
the vehicle makes a loud "clunking" sound
the vehicle surges forward or slows down unexpectedly
the check engine light illuminates
and the transmission warning light appears on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the Continuously Variable Transmission (CVT) can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle hesitates or fails to shift gears
the transmission slips or jerks
the vehicle makes a loud "clunking" sound
the vehicle surges forward or slows down unexpectedly
the check engine light illuminates
and the transmission warning light appears on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission slipping or jerking can cause the vehicle to lose power or stall, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle hesitates or fails to shift gears
the transmission slips or jerks
the vehicle makes a loud "clunking" sound
the vehicle surges forward or slows down unexpectedly
and the check engine light illuminates.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The deteriorating dashboard material can cause a sticky and shiny surface, creating glare and impeding the driver's ability to see, which can lead to accidents. Additionally, the release of small parts of black dashboard material can be a health hazard.
symptoms: The dashboard feels sticky or soft
has a shiny surface
and releases small parts of black material. The glare from the dashboard can be distracting and impede the driver's ability to see.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The sudden explosion of the panoramic sunroof can cause a loud noise, shatter glass, and create a hazardous driving condition, potentially leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The panoramic sunroof suddenly explodes
causing a loud noise
shattering glass
and creating a hazardous driving condition.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle's battery light and brake light come on simultaneously
the vehicle loses power and hesitates
the vehicle stalls
the key light blinks
and the vehicle is unable to start.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door lock actuator can cause the doors to malfunction, making it difficult or impossible to lock or unlock the doors.
symptoms: The doors won't lock
the door lock actuator fails
and the driver's door is not responding to the remote.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to lose power and hesitate, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission messes up
the vehicle won't catch gears
the RPM stays put
and a loud whining noise is heard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the starter motor can cause the vehicle to not start, leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The starter motor fails
produces noise when stationary and in motion
and the check engine light is intermittent.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering and brake system can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents and injuries.
symptoms: The steering wheel turns with great ease
but the tires do not follow the command
the brakes do not work properly
and the vehicle collides with a fixed object.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the camera system can cause the driver to lose visibility, leading to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: The camera system fails to work
comes and goes
and is not reliable.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake light can cause other drivers to not be aware of the vehicle's braking, leading to accidents.
symptoms: The passenger's side brake light fails
and the brake light bulb needs to be replaced.
